      "settings": {
        "title": "226Nm PEAK TORQUE. CRUSH ANY SLOPE.",
        "description": "Dominate the vertical. With a brutal 226Nm of peak wheel torque, the MC01 Pro provides unparalleled low-end climbing authority. It sustains absolute traction across loose shale and steep forest walls, effortlessly converting electrical energy into pure hill-climbing dominance.",
