      "settings": {
        "title": "Playful by choice. Predictable by design.",
        "description": "Most bikes avoid excitement to stay safe. Flux X26 is engineered to manage excitement instead. Acceleration feels responsive, not jumpy. Handling feels lively, not nervous. You stay in control — even when you're having fun.",
