            "content": "<p>Industrial art meets elite performance. The MC01 Pro redefines the aesthetic benchmark by stripping away the unnecessary. Showcasing the signature AOTOS avant-garde industrial aesthetic, its sharp geometric armor and hyper-minimalist profile fuse modern sophistication with raw, mechanical heritage.</p>",
